ein improves overall strand condition, reinforcing weak areas for visibly stronger, resilient hair.</p></div><div class=animation-block-main-bottom-3><h2 class=animation-block-main-bottom-num>03</h2><h2 class=animation-block-main-bottom-head>Smooths &amp; Repairs Frizz</h2><p class=animation-block-main-bottom-text>Ideal for damaged, porous strands&mdash;this formula reduces frizz, smooths texture, and strengthens hair by sealing split ends and restoring softness.</p></div><div class=animation-block-main-bottom-4><h2 class=animation-block-main-bottom-num>04</h2><h2 class=animation-block-main-bottom-head>Balances Moisture Levels</h2><p class=animation-block-main-bottom-text>Over-moisturized hair? Rice protein helps rebalance and protect against hygral fatigue, bringing hair back to a healthy moisture-strength equilibrium.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>
